"```sql\nSELECT DISTINCT disp.client_id\nFROM trans\nINNER JOIN disp ON trans.account_id = disp.account_id\nWHERE trans.operation = 'VYBER KARTOU'\n  AND trans.amount < (SELECT AVG(amount) FROM trans WHERE trans.operation = 'VYBER KARTOU' AND strftime('%Y', trans.date) = '1998')\n  AND strftime('%Y', trans.date) = '1998';\n```"